| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1603 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 22f1bcfb-7c27-5392-a79d-45b286ccec6c"
